<title><title>Available</title></title>

<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem>
<para><link xlink:href="src/Interop/Container/ContainerInterface.php"><computeroutput>ContainerInterface</computeroutput></link>. <link linkend="_md_public_2glpi_2vendor_2container-interop_2container-interop_2docs_2_container_interface">Description</link> <link linkend="_md_public_2glpi_2vendor_2container-interop_2container-interop_2docs_2_container_interface-meta">Meta Document</link>. Describes the interface of a container that exposes methods to read its entries.</para>
</listitem><listitem>
<para><link linkend="_md_public_2glpi_2vendor_2container-interop_2container-interop_2docs_2_delegate-lookup"><emphasis>Delegate lookup feature</emphasis></link>. <link linkend="_md_public_2glpi_2vendor_2container-interop_2container-interop_2docs_2_delegate-lookup-meta">Meta Document</link>. Describes the ability for a container to delegate the lookup of its dependencies to a third-party container. This feature lets several containers work together in a single application.</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</section>
